    {
      "id": 12, "type": "Note", "pos": [40, -250], "size": [900, 210], "flags": {}, "order": 11, "mode": 0,
      "properties": { "text": "" },
      "widgets_values": ["EMBED -> RECOVER ROUNDTRIP\n\nPART A (top): extract a palette, build a prompt, and Metadata Embedder saves a PNG to ComfyUI/output with the prompt stored in a tEXt chunk.\n>>> RUN PART A FIRST - it writes ideogram_roundtrip_00001_.png\n\nPART B (bottom): Load Image With Prompt opens that saved file BY PATH and recovers the embedded prompt; the Validator re-checks it. Point 'image_path' at the file Part A wrote (adjust the _00001_ counter if your output folder already had ideogram_roundtrip files).\n\nThe Metadata Reader (bottom-left) is wired to the loaded TENSOR on purpose: it reports 'not found' because a ComfyUI IMAGE tensor carries NO metadata - which is exactly why the file-based Load Image With Prompt exists.\n\nNote: tEXt metadata only survives in PNG. Re-saving the file as JPEG destroys the embedded prompt. ShowText nodes are optional."],
      "color": "#432", "bgcolor": "#653", "title": "README"
    }
